      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">NItrogen occurs naturally both in the free and combined states. In the free state it is the major constituent of air, making up 78% by volume and 75.5% by weight. Regarding abundance in the Earth's crust, nitrogen is in 30th place, constituting </text>
